-- EU to Use All Powers to Ensure Hungary Compliance, Barroso Says
-- B y   J o n e s   H a y d e n
-- 2012-01-12T11:39:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/eu-to-use-all-powers-to-ensure-hungary-compliance-barroso-says.html
European Commission President  Jose
Barroso  said the European Union will use all its powers to
ensure that  Hungary  complies with EU norms and values.  “We will use all our powers to make sure that Hungary
complies with the principles and values and the rules of the
European Union,” Barroso told reporters today in Copenhagen.
“I’m confident we will achieve that.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
